&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://firebase.google.com/docs/firestore/security/get-started&quot;&gt;Documentation Firestore Security Rules&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
